      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REALITY OLLIE (8) is yet to miss the placings here in an excellent record which boasts two wins. Comes off a (25.86) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Mix 6/7 over 460m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. OKAY BOSS (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 12 length third (26.20) over 460m at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to feature again. LOVES A CHAT (2) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that produced a quick 25.38 win over 450m at Shepparton. Has the ability and can find winning form again. LAKEVIEW LEIGH (7) is worth a look despite no experience at this circuit.",
